data.description: This could be your Florida dream home, check out 27249 Whitman Avenue in beautiful Harbour Heights! This 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 1773 square-foot house on a corner lot has been renovated within the last two years with a coastal grey palette. The kitchen and both bathrooms have been completely overhauled. The roof was installed in 2022. All the floors are now modern grey laminate. The spacious master bedroom has it's own ensuite bathroom and private office attached that has it's own entrance in the back; potentially could be made into a "mother in law suite". In the back yard there is a 14x11 shed with electricity ran to it. This house has size, room count, modern looks and amenities that will cater to your Florida home needs! Call today for more information or to book your private showing!
